comments: Mitchell (UTA) makes marginal contact with his off-arm to Covington's (HOU) side at the end of the drive.
Westbrook (HOU) slightly extends his right arm into Ingles' (UTA) path and makes some contact with Ingles' side as the pick is set.
Ingles (UTA) initiates contact with Harden's (HOU) right side/arm. The contact occurs prior to the start of Harden's upward shooting motion.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact across Mitchell's (UTA) front as he drives toward the lane.
Covington (HOU) makes marginal contact with Gobert's (UTA) side during rebounding.
Conley (UTA) extends his right leg into Harden's (HOU) path and initiates contact to Harden's lower half that affects his SQBR.
Tucker (HOU) and Mitchell (UTA) engage and disengage off-ball.
Mitchell (UTA) establishes his left foot as his pivot after receiving the pass and slides it as the pick approaches.
Gobert (UTA) is slightly late establishing himself in a screening position prior to marginal contact taking place with Westbrook (HOU).
Gobert (UTA) makes marginal contact with his left hand to Covington's (HOU) side as he moves to set the pick and does not deliver any further contact thereafter.
Harden (HOU) makes marginal contact with Clarkson's (UTA) backside after Clarkson picks up his dribble inside the perimeter.
Mitchell (UTA) slightly extends his hand against Tucker's (HOU) front as the pass is made, but the contact is marginal.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Tucker's (HOU) path and does not deliver the contact.
Mitchell (UTA) extends his off-arm and delivers contact to Covington's (HOU) side that dislodges him from position.
Tucker (HOU) initiates contact across Mitchell's (UTA) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Clarkson (UTA) makes marginal body contact during and at the end of Harden's (HOU) drive toward the lane.
Ingles (UTA) makes marginal contact with Harden's (HOU) right wrist as Harden passes the ball.
Clarkson (UTA) makes marginal body contact with Westbrook (HOU) during his drive into the lane.
Harden (HOU) and Gobert (UTA) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Tucker (HOU) and Mitchell (UTA) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Harden (HOU) and Mitchell (UTA) engage and disengage during the inbound.
Tucker (HOU) brushes Bogdanovic (UTA) and doesn't affect his natural shooting motion on his jump shot.
